{"id":"other/syllables","title":"syllables","contents":"<h1 id=\"音節\">音節</h1>\n<h2 id=\"音節の区切り方\">音節の区切り方</h2>\n<pre><code>- 1つの音節に含まれる母音の数は1つ\n- 長母音\n  - eaやawのなどの発音記号に:が含まれる母音は1つとカウント\n- 二重母音\n  - eiやoaなどの2つの母音が合わさったような発音になる場合は1つにカウント\n- 三重母音\n  - ireやourのなどの3つの母音が合わさったような発音になる場合は1つにカウント\n- 例外のE\n  - 単語の最後の文字がEで読まない場合は母音としてカウントしない\n- 例外のL\n  - 「子音 + L + 読まないE」はLを母音としてカウントする\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"one-syllable\">One syllable</h2>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  Tea\n</word-example>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  Quit\n</word-example>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  pay\n</word-example>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  drive\n</word-example>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  good\n</word-example>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  come\n</word-example>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  out\n</word-example>\n\n<h2 id=\"two-syllables-名詞-形容詞編\">Two syllables　名詞　形容詞編</h2>\n<pre><code>  1音節目を強調する\n</code></pre>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  swimming\n</word-example>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  apple\n</word-example>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  happy\n</word-example>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  rainbow\n</word-example>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  pretty\n</word-example>\n\n<h2 id=\"two-syllables-動詞\">Two syllables　動詞</h2>\n<pre><code>  2音節目を強調する\n</code></pre>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  begin\n</word-example>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  deserve\n</word-example>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  agree\n</word-example>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  protect\n</word-example>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  produce\n</word-example>\n\n<h2 id=\"three-syllables\">Three syllables</h2>\n<pre><code>  “-er”, “-or”, “-ly” or “-y”は最初の音節にストレス\n</code></pre>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  energy\n</word-example>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  finally\n</word-example>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  monitor\n</word-example>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  easier\n</word-example>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  silently\n</word-example>\n\n\n<h2 id=\"four-syllables\">Four syllables</h2>\n<pre><code>  “-cy”, “-ty”, “-phy”, “-gy” or “-al”は2音節にストレス\n</code></pre>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  dependency\n</word-example>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  photography\n</word-example>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  equality\n</word-example>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  democracy\n</word-example>\n<word-example pronaunce=\"\">\n  apology\n</word-example>\n\n<h2 id=\"参考動画\">参考動画</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ncEDve70xJM&amp;\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ncEDve70xJM&amp;</a></li>\n</ul>\n"}